<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Bean Haven Coffee</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>Bean Haven Coffee</h1>

<nav>
<button class="menu-toggle">☰ Menu</button>
<ul class="nav-links">
<li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
<li><a href="#menu">Menu</a></li>
<li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
</ul>
</nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
<img src="coffee.jpg" alt="Cup of freshly brewed coffee">
<h2>Your Daily Coffee Stop</h2>
<p>Fresh roasted beans and handcrafted drinks.</p>
<button>Order Online</button>
</section>

<section id="about">
<h2>About Us</h2>
<p>Bean Haven Coffee is a small neighborhood café focused on quality coffee and a welcoming atmosphere.</p>
</section>

<section id="menu">
<h2>Popular Drinks</h2>

<div class="menu-item">
<h3>Latte</h3>
<p>Smooth espresso with steamed milk.</p>
</div>

<div class="menu-item">
<h3>Cappuccino</h3>
<p>Rich espresso topped with foam.</p>
</div>

<div class="menu-item">
<h3>Iced Coffee</h3>
<p>Cold brewed for a refreshing taste.</p>
</div>

</section>

<section id="contact">
<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>Email: info@beanhaven.com</p>
<p>Phone: (555) 123-4567</p>
</section>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 Bean Haven Coffee</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
